# Architecture Compass

You are working on **A Step Forward**, an AI-native learning center.

Before non-trivial work, you **must** have read:

- `PLAN.md` — vision, stack, agents, memory, MCPs, hooks, skills, roadmap.
- `ARCHITECTURE.md` — components and data flows.
- `AGENTS.md` — runtime agent roster + Cursor sub-agent briefs.
- The relevant sub-agent brief in `.cursor/subagent-briefs/`.
- Any project skill the brief points to (under `skills/`).

If your task is large or ambiguous and not covered by the plan, **stop and ask** rather than improvise. Architectural decisions are made by Opus and recorded as ADRs under `docs/adr/`.

Monorepo map (memorize):

```
apps/web         — Next.js 15 frontend
apps/api         — FastAPI gateway
services/        — memory, graphrag, orchestrator, workers
packages/        — agents, schemas, ui
mcp-servers/     — memory, graphrag, curriculum, progress
prompts/         — versioned agent prompts
evals/           — promptfoo + DeepEval suites
infra/           — docker-compose, alembic
skills/          — project skills (sub-agent readable)
```
